title: A Tale of Perfect Street Style Accessories From London Fashion Week
text:
Street Style Accessories at London Fashion Week Fall 2017 A Tale of Perfect Street Style Accessories From London Fashion Week February 21, 2017 Share This Link Copy What’s Your Reaction? Thanks for your reaction Don’t forget to share this with your friends! ← Use Arrows Keys → 1 A Tale of Perfect Street Style Accessories From London Fashion Week 
The streets of London rang out with an unapologetically stylish greeting as Fashion Week kicked off under Big Ben's watchful eye. As for us, we have our sights set on the real street style stars (and have plans of promptly making them our own). Bold colors, unexpected details, and updated silhouettes swept the streets. Shoes varied, with sneakers and heeled booties in constant rotation. Bags were textured and floral, while outerwear was colorful and bold in equal measure. Take a look at what's inspiring our bag and shoe wish list here.
